data.text:
The Metrolinx Weston Subdivision begins at Union Station in Toronto and is 16.8 miles in length. At mile 16.8, the subdivision meets the CN Halton Sub. At one point the Weston Subdivision was owned by CN, and is still listed in their timetables as of September 2020.
